at this point.
Eighty-two?

07:13.400 --> 07:15.368
[ Sighs ]
I don't know.

07:15.469 --> 07:17.538
Don't touch those.

07:20.574 --> 07:23.844
[ Sighs ]
Look,

07:23.944 --> 07:26.680
I'm just gonna
be straight with you.

07:26.780 --> 07:30.584
Do you think
you're Cedar Heights
Shop and Save material?

07:30.684 --> 07:33.987
