become a part
of this family?

07:34.087 --> 07:38.458
- I don't know.
I guess I do.
- You guess you do?

07:38.559 --> 07:39.927
Yeah.
You guess?

07:40.027 --> 07:42.062
Okay. Well, look--

07:42.162 --> 07:44.431
Peter?
Yeah. Peter.

07:44.532 --> 07:46.433
I'm just gonna
be honest with you.

07:46.534 --> 07:48.869
