lined up around the block.
Not today--

07:53.406 --> 07:55.275
Okay. Well, thanks
for your time.

07:55.375 --> 07:58.546
Well-- No, no. Okay.

07:58.646 --> 08:01.982
- Mike.
- Hey, Robert.

08:02.082 --> 08:04.417
