of this place all of a sudden
be millionaires.

10:39.006 --> 10:42.776
Right?
I'll-- I'll think
about it, yeah.

10:42.876 --> 10:46.079
Hey, do you want, uh,
one of these?

10:46.179 --> 10:49.349
Take it home?
Give it to someone
you care about?

10:51.685 --> 10:53.854
Maybe another time.

10:53.954 --> 10:58.892
- Uh-huh. All right.
- Well, good-bye for now.

10:58.992 --> 11:02.629
Okay. Hey, do you want
a ride home today
or anything?

11:02.730 --> 11:06.734
Uh, no. I feel
like walking. Yeah.

11:07.667 --> 11:09.803
- All right.
- Bye.

11:55.315 --> 11:58.485
