- Your car is crashed
into the garage.

12:39.059 --> 12:43.463
Yeah.
I just wanted to make sure
that everything was all right.

12:43.563 --> 12:45.966
And then the door was open.
Yeah, the door was open.

12:46.066 --> 12:48.368
But that doesn't mean
you walk into somebody's house.
All right, I'm sorry.

12:48.468 --> 12:50.270
Please, I promise you.

12:50.370 --> 12:53.306
Wait, wait.
Just wait. Wait. Wait.
Huh?

12:53.406 --> 12:57.077
Wait. Who are you?

12:59.312 --> 13:01.949
My name is Mary.

13:04.417 --> 13:07.387
My name is Robert Malone.

13:08.555 --> 13:11.124
Nice to meet you,
Robert.

13:13.760 --> 13:15.863
Nice to meet you.

13:18.798 --> 13:20.733
This is a funny thing.

13:20.834 --> 13:23.070
Yes, it is.
[ Laughing ]

13:28.308 --> 13:31.144
Well--
Well, I should
be getting back.

13:31.244 --> 13:35.548
Yeah. Thanks
for checking on me.

13:35.648 --> 13:37.817
Of course.

13:38.886 --> 13:41.354
Bye.
Well--

13:41.454 --> 13:43.390
Bye.
Bye.

13:49.262 --> 13:51.098
[ Door Closes ]

13:58.705 --> 14:00.840
Good-bye.

14:04.277 --> 14:06.279
[ Exhales ]

14:09.482 --> 14:11.551
