14:17.457 --> 14:19.159
Robert.

14:19.259 --> 14:21.128
Mary.

14:21.228 --> 14:22.896
Yes.

14:22.996 --> 14:25.232
Hi.
I was just wondering--

14:25.332 --> 14:28.168
Um, I don't know.
This may sound crazy.

14:28.268 --> 14:29.836
But I-- Um,

14:29.937 --> 14:32.872
could we have dinner
together tomorrow?

14:32.973 --> 14:36.143
Uh-- I was--
[ Stammering ]

14:36.243 --> 14:38.311
I was--

14:38.411 --> 14:39.712
[ Stammering ]

14:39.812 --> 14:42.549
I'm sorry. Don't--
I made a mistake.

14:42.649 --> 14:44.851
- Excuse me.
- But-But-But--
No, no, no.

14:44.952 --> 14:46.987
But-- No, no.
Please, stop. Stop.

14:47.087 --> 14:49.022
Please.
Please stop. Wait.

14:50.690 --> 14:53.160
- Yes.
- Yes?

14:53.260 --> 14:55.028
Yes.

14:55.128 --> 14:57.965
We should have dinner
together tomorrow.

14:58.065 --> 14:59.866
- Oh, great.
- Great.

14:59.967 --> 15:02.069
Okay.
Okay.

15:02.169 --> 15:06.573
Um-- Should
I pick you up since--

15:08.408 --> 15:11.044
- Yeah. Yeah.
That would be good.
- Yeah.

15:11.144 --> 15:13.080
How did that happen?

15:13.180 --> 15:16.183
I had to use the restroom.

15:19.786 --> 15:23.156
Okay. I'll see you tomorrow.

15:25.658 --> 15:30.630
- Okay. See you tomorrow
at 6:00 to pick you up.
- Okay.

15:33.633 --> 15:35.068
Bye.

15:39.106 --> 15:41.108
- Robert.
- Yes?

15:41.208 --> 15:45.078
You should pick a place
for us to go on our date.

15:46.046 --> 15:48.681
- Date. Date.
- Yeah.

15:48.781 --> 15:50.517
Sure.

15:50.617 --> 15:52.819
Okay.

15:52.919 --> 15:55.322
- Night.
- Bye.

15:59.192 --> 16:01.628
- Robert?
- Yeah?

16:01.728 --> 16:04.064
I'm really glad we met.

16:05.065 --> 16:08.368
[ Chuckles ]
Me too.

16:09.869 --> 16:12.372
